hackathon-eligibility: Must be college/grad student to attend.
hackathon-requirements:
App Submission:
Simply include a short text description of your project and a few images, if applicable.
Do not include your project's source code.
hackathon-rules:
1. Project application must be to help others.
2. Project or aspect of project submitted/presented must be result only of work at Hack for Humanity.
